  "text": "In this section we describe the details of our experimental evaluation of our proposed framework. We evaluate our framework on KITTI dataset [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] and compare with prior art on both depth esimtation and surface normal estimation. Moreover, we present an ablation study to show the contribution of each component in our framework.",
